根据定义，我们有
$$\mathcal{B}\equiv M_p^2\frac{B_{\zeta}(k,k,k)}{\mathcal{P}_{\zeta}(k)}\,. $$ 
使用给定的双谱振幅，
$$B_{\zeta}(k,k,k)=-\frac{\pi^2\mathcal{P}_{\zeta}(k)}{2M_p^2}\left(\frac{c+1}{c+4}\right)\frac{\epsilon_V-2\eta_V}{\epsilon_V}\,, $$ 
我们得到
$$\mathcal{B}
= M_p^2\frac{-\frac{\pi^2\mathcal{P}_{\zeta}(k)}{2M_p^2}\left(\frac{c+1}{c+4}\right)\frac{\epsilon_V-2\eta_V}{\epsilon_V}}
{\mathcal{P}_{\zeta}(k)}
=-\frac{\pi^2}{2}\left(\frac{c+1}{c+4}\right)\frac{\epsilon_V-2\eta_V}{\epsilon_V}\,. $$

对于二次势 $V(\phi)=\frac{1}{2}m^2\phi^2$，慢滚参数为
$$\epsilon_V=\frac{M_p^2}{2}\left(\frac{V'}{V}\right)^2
=\frac{M_p^2}{2}\left(\frac{m^2\phi}{\frac{1}{2}m^2\phi^2}\right)^2
=\frac{2M_p^2}{\phi^2}\,, 
\quad
\eta_V=M_p^2\frac{V''}{V}
=M_p^2\frac{m^2}{\frac{1}{2}m^2\phi^2}
=\frac{2M_p^2}{\phi^2}\,, $$
因此 $\eta_V=\epsilon_V$。于是
$$\frac{\epsilon_V-2\eta_V}{\epsilon_V}
=\frac{\epsilon_V-2\epsilon_V}{\epsilon_V}
=-1\,. $$
代回原式得到
$$\mathcal{B}
=-\frac{\pi^2}{2}\left(\frac{c+1}{c+4}\right)(-1)
=\frac{\pi^2}{2}\frac{c+1}{c+4}\,. $$
